************************************************************************
*     Requirements
************************************************************************

=== General ===
 - cmake
 - gcc
 - boost
  
  
=== Voronoi & delaunay computation ===
 - cgal
 
 
=== Fast fourier transform and GPU parallelization ===
 - fftw
  
  
=== Graphs file output ===
 - libpng
 - cairo (optional)
  
  
=== Documentation ===
 - doxygen
 - graphViz
  


************************************************************************
*     Intallation
************************************************************************

=== Linux & Mac ===
 
$> cmake .
$> make
$> sudo make install

Optional :
$> make doc


